# Punch Card Project Release Notes

## Version 0.6.9 (2024-02-14)
- Enhanced statistics panel with improved layout and visibility
- Added real-time statistics tracking for punch card operations
- Improved text field sizing and alignment in statistics window
- Added automatic refresh of statistics every 5 seconds
- Fixed padding and margin issues in statistics display
- Improved error handling and logging for statistics tracking
- Added support for saving and loading statistics between sessions

Note: Please add a screenshot of the statistics panel to docs/images/stats_panel_0.6.9.png

